@startuml
!theme mono

title MONITOR 서비스 - Entity Relationship Diagram

!define TABLE(name,desc) class name as "desc" << (T,#FFAAAA) >>
!define PK(x) <b>x</b>
!define FK(x) <i>x</i>
!define UNIQUE(x) <u>x</u>

TABLE(monitoring_targets, "MONITORING_TARGETS\n(모니터링 대상)") {
    PK(id: VARCHAR(36))
    --
    place_id: VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL
    trip_id: VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL
    UNIQUE(schedule_item_id: VARCHAR(36)) NOT NULL
    user_id: VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL
    visit_datetime: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
    lat: NUMERIC(10,7) NOT NULL
    lng: NUMERIC(10,7) NOT NULL
    category: VARCHAR(50)
    --
    current_status: VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'GREY'
    current_status_updated_at: TIMESTAMPTZ
    consecutive_failure_count: INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
    --
    created_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
}

TABLE(status_history, "STATUS_HISTORY\n(상태 이력 - append-only)") {
    PK(id: VARCHAR(36))
    --
    place_id: VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL
    schedule_item_id: VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL
    status: VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL
    reason: TEXT
    judgment_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
    confidence_score: NUMERIC(4,3)
}

TABLE(collected_data, "COLLECTED_DATA\n(수집 원본 데이터)") {
    PK(id: VARCHAR(36))
    --
    place_id: VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL
    business_status: VARCHAR(20)
    precipitation_prob: INTEGER
    weather_condition: VARCHAR(50)
    walking_minutes: INTEGER
    transit_minutes: INTEGER
    distance_m: INTEGER
    congestion_level: VARCHAR(20)
    has_fallback: BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE
    --
    collected_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
}

' 논리적 관계 (FK 없음 - 서비스 내 독립)
monitoring_targets "1" ..o{ status_history : "place_id (논리적 참조)"
monitoring_targets "1" ..o{ collected_data : "place_id (논리적 참조)"

note top of monitoring_targets
  <b>Indexes:</b>
  • idx_monitoring_targets_place_id (place_id)
  • idx_monitoring_targets_visit_datetime (visit_datetime)
  • idx_monitoring_targets_user_id (user_id)
  • idx_monitoring_targets_schedule_item_id UNIQUE

  <b>Check Constraints:</b>
  • current_status IN ('GREEN','YELLOW','RED','GREY')

  <b>External References (no FK):</b>
  • place_id → PLACE.places.id
  • trip_id → SCHEDULE.trips.id
  • schedule_item_id → SCHEDULE.schedule_items.id
  • user_id → AUTH.users.id

  <b>Trigger:</b>
  ScheduleItemAddedEvent 수신 시 등록
end note

note right of status_history
  <b>Indexes:</b>
  • idx_status_history_place_id_judgment_at
    (place_id, judgment_at DESC)
  • idx_status_history_schedule_item_id
  • idx_status_history_judgment_at

  <b>Check Constraints:</b>
  • status IN ('GREEN','YELLOW','RED','GREY')
  • confidence_score BETWEEN 0.000 AND 1.000

  <b>Retention Policy:</b>
  • Append-only (UPDATE/DELETE 금지)
  • 월별 RANGE 파티셔닝
  • 6개월 경과 → S3 아카이빙 후 삭제
  • ML 학습 데이터 소스 [T4]
end note

note bottom of collected_data
  <b>Indexes:</b>
  • idx_collected_data_place_id_collected_at
    (place_id, collected_at DESC)

  <b>Design Note:</b>
  • 폴백 캐시 역할 (수집 실패 시 재사용)
  • 외부 API: Google Places, OpenWeatherMap,
    Google Directions
end note

legend right
  <b>Redis Cache (DB 4):</b>
  mntr:badge:{placeId}      TTL 5분
  mntr:collected:{placeId}  TTL 30분
  mntr:status:{placeId}     TTL 5분

  <b>Events Published:</b>
  PlaceStatusChangedEvent → BRIEFING, ALTERNATIVE

  <b>Legend:</b>
  PK = Primary Key
  .. = 논리적 참조 (DB FK 없음)
end legend

@enduml
